description: Proudly offering a charming updated two bed, one and a half bath single family home.  The property is situated in a highly sought after South Boston location and is in walking distance to the beach, Thomas Park, shops, restaurants and public transport.  This house offers a newly installed chef's kitchen including stainless steel appliances, custom cabinets, granite counter tops,  recently renovated baths, hardwood floors, full size laundry, central heat and air conditioning, basement storage, great fenced in outdoor space with deck and stone patio.
